column3: When are you moving to Copenhagen so we can teach you about bike culture?!? Denmark needs great CRPG makers Josh!!! And education, healthcare and pension are supplied by government here. Not too far from Germany so you can take the bike down there to work on your German Fetish as well. Denmark needs Josh! Come on man. We won the Tour de France one year (okay he was banged up on doping just like Lance).Â
this is the most immersive video game developer bicycling enthusiast simulator ive ever seen thanks for the upload
